{"title":"Servlet生命周期","uid":"515fd95418d4a8e087bd7d6f4dc47d21","slug":"Servlet生命周期","date":"2023-06-18T04:49:37.000Z","updated":"2023-06-18T08:57:52.653Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Servlet生命周期.json","keywords":null,"cover":"/images/Servlet生命周期/Servlet生命周期.png","content":"<h1 id=\"Servlet生命周期\"><a href=\"#Servlet生命周期\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Servlet生命周期\"></a>Servlet生命周期</h1><p>Servlet程序是运行在服务器短的一段Java程序，其生命周期将受到Web容器的控制。生命周期包括：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>加载程序</li>\n<li>初始化</li>\n<li>服务</li>\n<li>销毁</li>\n<li>卸载</li>\n</ol>\n<p><img src=\"/../images/Servlet%E7%94%9F%E5%91%BD%E5%91%A8%E6%9C%9F/Servlet%E7%94%9F%E5%91%BD%E5%91%A8%E6%9C%9F.png\"></p>\n<p>Servlet生命周期对应的方法：</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>方法</th>\n<th>描述</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td>public void init() throws ServletException</td>\n<td>Servlet初始化时调用</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>public void init(ServletConfig config) throws ServletException</td>\n<td>Servlet初始化时调用，可以通过ServletConfig 读取配置信息</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>public abstract void service(ServletRequest req, ServletResponse res) throws ServletException, IOException</td>\n<td>Servlet服务，一般不会直接重写此方法，而是使用doGet()或doPost()方法</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>public void destroy()</td>\n<td>Servlet销毁时调用</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<h2 id=\"加载Servlet\"><a href=\"#加载Servlet\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"加载Servlet\"></a>加载Servlet</h2><p>Web容器负责加载Servlet，当Web容器启动时或者是在第一次使用这个Servlet时，容器会负责创建Servlet实例，但是用户必须通过部署描述符（web.xml）指定Servlet的位置（Servlet所在的包.类名称），成功加载后，Web容器会通过反射的方式对Servlet进行实例化。</p>\n<h2 id=\"初始化\"><a href=\"#初始化\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"初始化\"></a>初始化</h2><p>当一个Servlet被实例化后，容器将调用<code>init()</code>方法初始化这个对象，初始化的目的是为了让Servlet对象在处理客户端请求前完成一些初始化工作，如建立数据库连接、读取资源文件信息等，如果初始化失败，则此Servlet将被直接卸载。</p>\n<h2 id=\"处理服务\"><a href=\"#处理服务\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"处理服务\"></a>处理服务</h2><p>当有请求提交时，Servlet将调用<code>service()</code>方法，（常用的是<code>doGet()</code>和<code>doPost()</code>）进行处理。在<code>service()</code>方法中，Servlet可以通过<code>ServletRequest</code>接收客户的请求，也可以利用<code>ServletResponse</code>设置响应信息。</p>\n<h2 id=\"销毁\"><a href=\"#销毁\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"销毁\"></a>销毁</h2><p>当Web容器关闭或者检测到一个Servlet要从容器中被删除时，会自动调用<code>destroy()</code>方法，以便让该实例释放掉所占用的资源。</p>\n<h2 id=\"卸载\"><a href=\"#卸载\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"卸载\"></a>卸载</h2><p>当一个Servlet调用完<code>destroy()</code>方法后，此实例将等待被垃圾收集器所回收，如果需要再次使用此Servlet时，会重写调用<code>init()</code>方法初始化。</p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>在正常情况下，Servlet只会初始化一次，而处理服务会调用多次，销毁也只会调用一次。但是如果一个Servlet长时间不使用的话，也会被容器自动销毁，而如果需要再次使用时会重写进行初始化操作，即在特殊情况下初始化可能进行多次，销毁也可能进行多次。</p></blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"示例\"><a href=\"#示例\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"示例\"></a>示例</h2><p>index.jsp：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-jsp\" data-language=\"jsp\"><code class=\"language-jsp\">&lt;%@ page contentType&#x3D;&quot;text&#x2F;html; charset&#x3D;UTF-8&quot; pageEncoding&#x3D;&quot;UTF-8&quot; %&gt;\n&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\n&lt;html&gt;\n&lt;head&gt;\n    &lt;title&gt;Servlet生命周期&lt;&#x2F;title&gt;\n&lt;&#x2F;head&gt;\n&lt;body&gt;\n&lt;a href&#x3D;&quot;life&quot;&gt;life servlet&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;\n&lt;&#x2F;body&gt;\n&lt;&#x2F;html&gt;</code></pre>\n\n<p>LifeCycleServlet.java：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-java\" data-language=\"java\"><code class=\"language-java\">package cn.cukor.javawebstudy;\n\nimport jakarta.servlet.ServletException;\nimport jakarta.servlet.annotation.WebServlet;\nimport jakarta.servlet.http.HttpServlet;\nimport jakarta.servlet.http.HttpServletRequest;\nimport jakarta.servlet.http.HttpServletResponse;\n\nimport java.io.IOException;\n\n@WebServlet(&quot;&#x2F;life&quot;)\npublic class LifeCycleServlet extends HttpServlet &#123;\n    @Override\n    public void init() throws ServletException &#123;\n        System.out.println(&quot;Servlet 初始化 --&gt; init&quot;);\n    &#125;\n\n    @Override\n    protected void doGet(HttpServletRequest req, HttpServletResponse resp) throws ServletException, IOException &#123;\n        System.out.println(&quot;Servlet 服务 --&gt; doGet() 、 doPost()&quot;);\n    &#125;\n\n    @Override\n    protected void doPost(HttpServletRequest req, HttpServletResponse resp) throws ServletException, IOException &#123;\n        this.doGet(req, resp);\n    &#125;\n\n    @Override\n    public void destroy() &#123;\n        System.out.println(&quot;Servlet 销毁 --&gt; destroy()&quot;);\n    &#125;\n&#125;</code></pre>\n\n\n\n<p>效果：</p>\n<p><img src=\"/../images/Servlet%E7%94%9F%E5%91%BD%E5%91%A8%E6%9C%9F/image-20230618132321144.png\" alt=\"image-20230618132321144\"></p>\n<p>当点击了页面的超链接的时候，IDEA的终端会打印下面的内容：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">Servlet ��ʼ�� --&gt; init\nServlet ���� --&gt; doGet() �� doPost()</code></pre>\n\n<p>然后在当前页面刷新，IDEA终端会打印下面的内容：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">Servlet ���� --&gt; doGet() �� doPost()</code></pre>\n\n<p>当关闭服务后，IDEA终端会打印下面的内容：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">Servlet ���� --&gt; destroy()</code></pre>\n\n<p>这里出现乱码先不用管，这个是字符集不一致导致的。</p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>在这里需要注意的是，如果<code>LifeCycleServlet</code>类中重写了<code>service()</code>方法，则对应的<code>doGet()</code>或<code>doPost()</code>方法就不再起作用，而是直接使用<code>service()</code>方法进行处理。因为在<code>HttpServlet</code>类中已经将<code>service()</code>方法重写，方法的主要功能就是区分不同的请求类型，如果是get请求则自动调用<code>doGet()</code>方法，如果是post请求则自动调用<code>doPost()</code>，实际上Servlet程序本身就是Java模板设计模式的应用。</p></blockquote>\n","feature":true,"text":"Servlet生命周期Servlet程序是运行在服务器短的一段Java程序，其生命周期将受到Web容器的控制。生命周期包括： 加载程序 初始化 服务 销毁 卸载 Servlet生命周期对应的方法： 方法 描述 public void init() throws ServletEx...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"3.1k","symbolsTime":"3 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"Servlet","slug":"Servlet","count":6,"path":"api/categories/Servlet.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Java","slug":"Java","count":21,"path":"api/tags/Java.json"},{"name":"Servlet","slug":"Servlet","count":6,"path":"api/tags/Servlet.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Servlet%E7%94%9F%E5%91%BD%E5%91%A8%E6%9C%9F\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Servlet生命周期</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%8A%A0%E8%BD%BDServlet\"><span class=\"toc-text\">加载Servlet</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%88%9D%E5%A7%8B%E5%8C%96\"><span class=\"toc-text\">初始化</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1\"><span class=\"toc-text\">处理服务</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E9%94%80%E6%AF%81\"><span class=\"toc-text\">销毁</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%8D%B8%E8%BD%BD\"><span class=\"toc-text\">卸载</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%A4%BA%E4%BE%8B\"><span class=\"toc-text\">示例</span></a></li></ol></li></ol>","author":{"name":"CukorZhong","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"/images/logo.jpg","link":"/","description":"一个对计算机技术非常热爱的程序员","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{"bilibili":{"icon":"/images/bilibili-svgrepo-com.svg","link":"https://space.bilibili.com/1117276308"},"csdn":{"icon":"/images/csdn.svg","link":"https://blog.csdn.net/qq_53744721"}}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{"title":"Servlet获取内置对象","uid":"391c7161b3ebb766451753feb21e8bbb","slug":"Servlet获取内置对象","date":"2023-06-18T06:39:33.000Z","updated":"2023-06-18T08:57:03.620Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Servlet获取内置对象.json","keywords":null,"cover":"/images/Servlet获取内置对象/image-20230618150803578.png","text":"Servlet获取内置对象在之前的程序中，使用Servlet可以取得request、response、config对象，实际上通过Servlet程序也可以取得session及application的内置对象。 获取HttpSession实例在Servlet程序中要想取得一个ses...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"4.2k","symbolsTime":"4 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"Servlet","slug":"Servlet","count":6,"path":"api/categories/Servlet.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Java","slug":"Java","count":21,"path":"api/tags/Java.json"},{"name":"Servlet","slug":"Servlet","count":6,"path":"api/tags/Servlet.json"}],"author":{"name":"CukorZhong","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"/images/logo.jpg","link":"/","description":"一个对计算机技术非常热爱的程序员","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{"bilibili":{"icon":"/images/bilibili-svgrepo-com.svg","link":"https://space.bilibi